data.name: label6.Text
data.value:
Construction Cost: is the number of materials the Constructor Agents will create to finish the construction
Clicking on the Edge's Names will open a small box where you can edit it's cost
Double Clicking the agent's box will open a new form to display it's inventory and jobs Single Clicking the site's box will open a new form to display it's inventory and current agents at the site
Skill level: will determine how quick the agent will do it's job. The higher the skill, the faster it is.
